                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-141-18680106 t18680106-141-punishment-33"></join>Nine Months' Imprisonment</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Justice Smith</hi>.</p>
